                           OFFICE ASSISTANT (G/T)
                        Change of Contact Information
     __________________________________________________________________

    To update the contact information on your Office Assistant (G/T) list
    eligibility for Sacramento/Yolo Counties, you must enter your PIN number,
    Candidate ID, and last name below, exactly as you entered them the Internet
    Application Process. Do not enter your first name or middle initial - just
    your last name.

   Note - You may use either upper or lower case characters when entering
   information or answers on this examination. The system will convert all
   lower case entries to upper case.

   Candidate ID: ______
   Last Name: _____________________
